txt.en: 'I am taking one last journey through Middle-earth before I sail into the West.'
'I plan to spend a few days visiting friends at Duillond, then I will come back to Celondim.'
'I will miss this land, but it is time for me to leave these shores. I am not sorrowful.'
'I have come a long way from Greenwood the Great, but there is still one journey left to me.'
